{"tid":1838722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔只醫護，應該全港大三罷！","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T09:13:13.000Z","uid":296491,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f29ebc45b2c133b43895cd7496b5223929614139","tid":1838722,"uid":296491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢做醫護好慘，做又唔係唔做又唔係<br />\n仲要搵命同你搏！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候我地要同醫護企埋一齊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而唔只係推醫護自己罷工！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷！</span></span><br />\n之前組織工會至今應該都儲左一定人力<br />\n個陣就話「搞工會搞罷工需要時間」<br />\n但到而家都幾個月啦！而且係最準確既時機！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">28號初四太遲！過埋新年就玩完！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫政府封關，要自救！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 與醫護同行，全港大三罷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了，要交稅俾政府！"},{"pid":"239fc279d9e4930865b581797b614b1dd5ed867c","tid":1838722,"uid":321194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca54e0b600234db0b789215f036f8e01fe803e4e","tid":1838722,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.</span>"},{"pid":"f97496335bcf96393397ba0ef29f89cd05905269","tid":1838722,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<